28 (6) For a statewide ballot question committee, file a pre-primary, pre-general, year-
29 end and, if applicable, supplemental report and amendments in even numbered
30 years and in odd numbered years, file a year-end and, if applicable, amendments:
31 (a) A pre-primary statement;
32 (b) A pre-general statement;
33 (c) A An annual year-end statement;
34 (d) A supplemental report as provided in § 12-27-28, if applicable; and
